          <cite class='member author entry-title'><a href="/people/mr-george-fyfe" title="Mr George Fyfe">Lord Fyfe of Fairfield</a></cite>
          <p class='first-para'>
            That is a very helpful reply from my noble friend. I beg leave to withdraw the amendment.
          </p>
        </blockquote>
      </div>
      
